  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f0b1b539fc98f524aa46fa3800d1f743, type: 3}
  Text: "Everything I want the world to be\r\nIs now coming true especially for me\r\nAnd
    the reason is clear, it's because you are here\r\nYou're the nearest thing to
    \nheaven \nthat I've seen\r\nI'm on the top of the world, \nlooking down on creation\r\nAnd
    the only \nexplanation \nI can find\r\nIs the love that I've found \never since
    you've been around\r\nYour love's put me at the top of the \nworld"
